data.description: 4 Bedrooms and 2 full bath cape cod style home that has been in the family since it was originally built. The hardwood floors and many fixtures are original to the home! Sitting on nearly half an acre of mature trees in Derry township, adjacent to Bull Frog valley park, this property is in a wonderful location close to everything Hershey can offer! Some improvements need to be made, but with some patience and elbow grease this home can be transformed into something very special.
